 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Mark Cuban tweeted</a>=
=C2=A0that =E2=80=9Cevery major tech company, Google, [Meta], et al. is on =
the phone with their antitrust lawyers asking if they can buy Twitter and g=
et it approved. And Twitter is on the phone with their lawyers asking which=
 can be their white knight.=E2=80=9D Meanwhile I <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27381871.266597/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
