r: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bor=
der-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #c=
cc;">doesn=E2=80=99t believe in them</a>? (=E2=80=9CThere is no way you unl=
ock the value of Twitter by making it 99.9% porn, fake Ray-Ban and male enh=
ancement ads,=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/c=
lick/27381871.266597/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9hbGV4c3RhbW9zL3N0YXR1cy8xNT=
